E. A. LYNCH, as Trustee in Bankruptcy of Estate of Earl L. White, Corporation, Limited, Bankrupt, Appellant, v. CITIZENS’ NAT. TRUST & SAVINGS BANK, Appellee. No. 6617. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 12, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and JAMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed without costs; mandate forthwith.
